        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-11 13:35:28.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nIs it necessary to create a zip file of the datarouter docker-compose data?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "fd11d6c75aa5bf6652557e3318ba1b052c95a630",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3395,
          "name": "Marcin Migdal",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "marcin.migdal@nokia.com",
          "username": "mmigdal"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-12 07:50:33.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nIn order to run DMaaP DR using docker compose, few files have to be\ncopied or created manuaaly. \nWhat i case you miss/forget about one?\nIt's easy to pack them into ZIP during maven build, save such zip at backend and download using wget during test automation or manual testing.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "56f51e50cd7e489903b8ae328979b4426cdd5c8e",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 4447,
          "name": "Conor Ward",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "conor.ward@est.tech",
          "username": "econwar"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-17 12:57:52.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> In order to run DMaaP DR using docker compose, few files have to be\n > copied or created manuaaly.\n > What i case you miss/forget about one?\n > It's easy to pack them into ZIP during maven build, save such zip\n > at backend and download using wget during test automation or manual\n > testing.\n\nSo this zip will now be built and stored in nexus, is that correct?",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "92d50777615711b48052c550c598af295fb794f6",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3395,
          "name": "Marcin Migdal",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "marcin.migdal@nokia.com",
          "username": "mmigdal"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2018-10-17 13:01:00.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nThis is first step - just create ZIP.\nI would like to have this ZIP to be kept at Nexus, but this will affect CI propobly. Same situation we have st PNF Simulator.\nSo my proposal is to add saving at Nexus as a second step.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
